 z←⎕UCS'UTF-8'⎕UCS enlist nul,¨,data
 :If ∨/m←~z∊ok
     (m/z)←↓'%',(⎕D,⎕A)[⍉16 16⊤⎕UCS m/z]
     data←(⍴data)⍴1↓¨{(⍵=nul)⊂⍵}enlist z
 :EndIf
     
 r←¯1↓enlist data,¨(⍴data)⍴'=&'
∇

